==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Inefficiency
<hw>In`ef*fi"cien*cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality
of being inefficient; lack of power or energy sufficient for the desired
effect; inefficacy; incapacity; <as>as, he was discharged from his
position for <ex>inefficiency</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inefficient</ent>⟦br⟧
